What is Copart?

Discover Copart - the leading platform for exceptional vehicle buying and selling experiences! We offer a wide catalog of used, salvageable and irretrievable vehicles, simplifying the process for our customers to find the vehicle of their dreams. At Copart we offer:

Purchase: Through auctions or, directly on the website, through Buy Now.
Sale: Copart Venda Meu Carro offers the opportunity to sell vehicles to individuals or companies. They can be sold at our auctions or directly on the Buy It Now in the website.

When you buy from Copart, we make the auction experience more exciting than ever! Our platform allows you to participate in dynamic auctions to ensure you win your favorite vehicle or, if you prefer, buy directly through our innovative "Buy It Now" feature, without the need for an auction.

Selling at Copart, we stand out by offering our customers the opportunity to maximize their results when selling their own vehicles with us through VMC (Sell My Car). We accept vehicles in any condition, as long as they are in good condition. And the best? At Copart, you have the flexibility to buy or sell according to your preferences! Whether through exciting auctions or "Buy It Now", where the decision is yours.

With the "Buy It Now" feature, we offer the convenience of purchasing vehicles instantly, without waiting for auctions. Total vehicle price ​​are clearly displayed, allowing you to make offers or buy immediately.

We serve a diverse audience, from used car buyers to dismantlers, dealers, repair shops and individuals. Explore our vast inventory, which includes cars, trucks, SUVs, motorcycles, equipment and VMC vehicles, available on our website.

Whether buying or selling, start your journey with us! Register now and participate in exciting online auctions or purchase vehicles directly through "Buy It Now". Copart is here to make your automotive experience unique and incredible!"

Cookie Overview and Settings

We disclose your personal information to advertising and analytics partners, social media platforms and other third parties for advertising and marketing purposes, including through the use of cookies and other tracking technologies. These activities may be considered a “sale”, “sharing” and/or “targeted advertising” under various U.S. state data privacy laws, including the CCPA. Depending on your state of residency, you may have the right to opt-out of having your information “sold,” “shared,” or used for “targeted advertising”.  You can set your privacy preferences by clicking the appropriate button below to toggle it to “On” or “Off”. To opt out of the sale or sharing of your personal information, disable the toggles next to "Targeting Cookies" and "Social Media Cookies" or click "Reject All" in this settings window.

We also honor browser-based Global Privacy Control (GPC) opt-out preference signals. If we have detected your GPC signal, we will automatically opt you out of targeted advertising cookies.
Cookie Policy

Manage Consent Preferences

Strictly Necessary Cookies

Always Active

These cookies are necessary for the website to function and cannot be switched off in our systems. They are usually only set in response to actions made by you which amount to a request for services, such as setting your privacy preferences, logging in or filling in forms. You can set your browser to block or alert you about these cookies, but some parts of the site will not then work. These cookies do not store any personally identifiable information.

Performance Cookies

Performance cookies are used in order to improve the quality of our website and its content. These types of cookies give us information about the behavior of our users and help us to identify and eliminate difficulties or errors in the use of our website. It also enables us to evaluate the efficiency of our advertising measures and improve the quality of the advertising that is displayed to our users.

Functional Cookies

These cookies enable the website to provide enhanced functionality and personalisation. They may be set by us or by third party providers whose services we have added to our pages. If you do not allow these cookies then some or all of these services may not function properly.

Targeting Cookies

These cookies may be set through our site by our advertising partners. They may be used by those companies to build a profile of your interests and show you relevant adverts on other sites. They do not store directly personal information, but are based on uniquely identifying your browser and internet device. If you do not allow these cookies, you will experience less targeted advertising.
